          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The targets were sealed under",
                "slight  negative pressure of He in quartz ampules (6.7",
                "x 51 mm). The sealed  quartz ampules were then placed",
                "in the welded Al rabbits (6.7 x 51  mm) for",
                "irradiation."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "GSPEC",
                "RCHEM"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " After the irradiation, the quartz",
                "samples were soaked in HNO3 to remove surface",
                "contamination. After the appropriate cooling time,",
                "the activities were measured at a 30 cm distance from",
                "a well-calibrated HPGe detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PGS"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " All activities were followed for several half-",
                "lives and the activities at the end of bombardment",
                "were extrapolated by the CLSQ code. When the multiple",
                "gamma-rays were used for assay, their intensities",
                "were used as weighing factors in calculations of the",
                "average activity values. The relevant nuclear data",
                "were taken from Lederer et al., Reus and Westmeier,",
                "and Mughabghab. The fission-averaged cross sections",
                "for the individual reactions, sigma, leading to",
                "117mSn, 119mSn and 195mPt were calculated by solving",
                "sets of three simultaneous equations for each",
                "radioisotope."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " It includes uncertainty due to counting",
                "statistics and detector efficiency. The uncertainty",
                "for thermal cross sections and resonance integrals",
                "includes"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "  5% error in thermal-to-epithermal ratio."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "This article contains data on fission-averaged",
                "cross sections for Oak Ridge High Flux Isotope",
                "Reactor (HFIR) spectrum and 116Sn(n,gamma),",
                "117Sn(n,n'), 118Sn(n,2n), 118Sn(n,gamma),",
                "119Sn(n,n'), 120Sn(n,2n), 194Pt(n,gamma), 195Pt(n,n')",
                "and 196Pt(n,2n) reactions. Unfortunately, these data",
                "are given for integral cross sections and Oak Ridge",
                "reactor neutron spectrum. This reactor neutron",
                "spectrum is not well defined, please see Table 2.",
                "Consequently, these data were not compiled."
              ]
            }
          ],
